<h6 class="byline"> <span class="en_byline">CHOE SANG-HUN</span> <span class="time"></span> </h6>
<div class="thumbnail">
	  <a href="/asia-pacific/20200622/north-korea-kim-yo-jong/zh-hant/" title="金與正的崛起對於朝鮮和世界意味著什麼？">
